\end_layout

\end_inset

explicitly recognizes the close affinity between the received theory of
 differential rent and his own marginalism: 
\begin_inset Quotes xld
\end_inset

The general correctness of the views put forth in the preceding chapters
 [of Jevons' book] derives great probability from their close resemblance
 to the Theory of Rent, as it has been accepted by English writers for nearly
 a century.
\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset


